---
layout: base.njk
title: Dr. Hadiza Galadima — Biostatistics, Public Health, Pedagogy
description: Dr. Hadiza Galadima — biostatistician at Old Dominion University. Research on statistical methods for public health, teaching of applied biostatistics, and open tools for students.
schemaType: Person
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">{{ site.affiliation.name }} · Biostatistician</p>
      <h1 class="hero-display">
        Dr. Hadiza <span class="hero-display-accent">Galadima</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-tagline">Statistical reasoning for public-health research &amp; pedagogy.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/research/" class="button button-primary button-arrow">Research</a>
        <a href="/teaching/" class="button button-ghost button-arrow">Teaching</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <figure class="hero-portrait">
      <img src="/assets/photo.svg" alt="Portrait of {{ site.name }}" width="400" height="500" loading="eager">
    </figure>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section practice">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">What I do</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three overlapping lines of work.</h2>
  </div>

  <article class="practice-item reveal">
    <div class="practice-number">01</div>
    <div class="practice-body">
      <h3><a href="/research/">Research</a></h3>
      <p class="practice-description">Methods and applied collaborations in public-health statistics — small-sample inference, outcome evaluation, and the statistical groundwork behind community-health programs.</p>
      <a href="/research/" class="practice-link">Publications &amp; interests</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="practice-item reveal">
    <div class="practice-number">02</div>
    <div class="practice-body">
      <h3><a href="/teaching/">Teaching</a></h3>
      <p class="practice-description">MPHO 605 (Biostatistics) at ODU, taught effect-sizes-first. Open-source calculators for students — no ads, no tracking, work shown — live at <a href="https://ztchi.hgaladima.com/" rel="noopener">ztchi.hgaladima.com</a>.</p>
      <a href="/teaching/" class="practice-link">Approach &amp; tools</a>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="practice-item reveal">
    <div class="practice-number">03</div>
    <div class="practice-body">
      <h3><a href="/blog/">Writing</a></h3>
      <p class="practice-description">Teaching notes, pedagogy reflections, research-in-progress essays. Unpolished on purpose — this is where ideas develop before they become papers or lectures.</p>
      <a href="/blog/" class="practice-link">Read the blog</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="reveal">
    <p class="section-eyebrow">Recent writing</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">From the blog.</h2>
  </div>

  <ul class="post-list reveal">
    {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | slice(0, 3) %}
      <li class="post-list-item">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-list-link">
          <span class="post-list-date"><time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time></span>
          <span class="post-list-text">
            <span class="post-list-title">{{ post.data.title }}</span>
            {% if post.data.summary %}<span class="post-list-summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</span>{% endif %}
          </span>
        </a>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <p style="margin-top: var(--space-xl);"><a href="/blog/" class="practice-link">All posts</a></p>
</section>
